name: Llogiq on stuff
body:
### What is this about?

I plan to write here about interesting things that I encounter, stuff I've coded, and whatever I feel like writing about.

Since I'm currently learning [Rust](https://http://www.rust-lang.org/), expect some content regarding this cool language. I also work in Java, so that may show up here and there, too.
